  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h4 class="modal-title">Add Save Slot Thumbnail</h4>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>The save slot thumbnail is a space representing a saved game. When the slot is used, an image taken from the game at the save point will be displayed. If the slot is free, the save slot thumbnail will be displayed. Save slot thumbnails are not mandatory to have many save slots, but they are good to help the player remember which slot is which. Combine the save slot thumbnail with save/load buttons to create the save/load menu.</p>
        <fieldset>
          <legend>Image file:</legend>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="input-group mb-3">
              <div class="custom-file">
                <input type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="image-input">
